The test flow is as follows:

1) Log in with a user that has admin rights

2) Invite a user with an email address that you receive emails from, e.g
siba+1@fastcomm.com

3) Wait for email invitation

4) Create new account with siba+1@fastcomm.com

5) Click on the Join via Token button in the Workspaces screen

6) Verify that the chats functionality works.
